  "abstracts": [
    {
      "note": "description",
      "abstract": "Prohibits any employer or employee from subjecting an employee to abusive conduct.  Requires employers and certain employees to take all reasonable preventative and responsive measures to ensure a safe work environment free of abusive conduct.  Prohibits employers and certain employees from taking retaliatory actions against employees who engage in certain protected acts.  Establishes a penalty, private cause of action, and remedies.  Requires the Department of Labor and Industrial Relations to adopt rules."
    }
  ],
